data.clean_description: Genuine UK Generic 300 mg caps Wockhardt. NPK type Calcium channel blocker blocks nerve transmission at a synaptic level. IMHO not useful as a recreational drug although some would argue otherwise Useful adjunct to an opioid taper particularly when stepping off low dose subutex buprenorphine. Also very useful in mitigating withdrawal from GBL or GHB. Prescibed usually for nerve pain or epilepsy.
data.name: Gabapentin 300mg caps x10
